What you need to know:  The purpose of the games is to give an opportunity to  employees from the 47 County Governments to exhibit their sporting talents and to interact and learn from each other’s cultural orientations.Since its inception, Kicosca games have been hosted in Nairobi, Nakuru, Uasin Gishu, Kiambu, Machakos, Kisii, Kericho and Embu.